# Shared Types and Utilities

## Purpose
This package contains shared TypeScript types and utilities that are used across multiple applications in the monorepo.

## Structure
- **types/**: Shared TypeScript interfaces and type definitions
- **utils/**: Utility functions (when added)
- **constants/**: Shared constants (when added)

## Usage
Import shared types using the universal alias:

```typescript
import { PhotoItem } from '@shared/types/PhotoItem';
import { PermissionStatus } from '@shared/types/PermissionStatus';
```

## TypeScript Configuration
- **No build step**: Source files are referenced directly
- **skipLibCheck**: Enabled to prevent conflicts with Vrite tooling
- **Composite project**: Part of the monorepo's project reference system